+Factory Reset Puzzle Solver - Implementation Complete
+
+Part 1: Toggle Puzzle (solveToggle)
+- Implemented using meet-in-the-middle technique to handle up to 40 buttons/lights efficiently.
+- Returns the lexicographically smallest set of button indices with minimal presses.
+- Verified with unit tests and random stress tests.
+
+Part 2: Counter Puzzle (solveCounter)
+- Solves linear system over GF(modulus) using Gaussian elimination.
+- Handles up to 40 counters/buttons, modulus up to 97 (prime).
+- Returns the press counts with minimal total presses and lexicographically smallest.
+- Uses meet-in-the-middle on null space when dimension is large.
+
+All tests pass, linting passes, and stress tests show no failures.
+
+The solution is ready in src/index.ts.
